name: CUBED (FofothelegendYT)
description:
CUBED is a browser game made in 5 hours as a "fun" challenge in scratch and it didn't turn out to be "fun"

A or left arrow to go left and d or right arrow to go left and s or down arrow to squish

get away from the cube-orites and the flashing yellow bolts or GET CUBED!

Made in scratch
